<DOCNO>52605_55</DOCNO>
<TEXT>Sporting teams in Port Talbot include:
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>52605_56</DOCNO>
<TEXT>The town is part of the Ospreys rugby union region, by which it is represented at the top level of the sport.
</TEXT>
</DOC>
